<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RTI Application</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 1in;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 6.5in;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24pt;
            margin-bottom: 0.5in;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 0.2in;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .underline {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 0.75in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 3in;
            margin-top: 0.2in;
            padding-top: 0.05in;
        }
        .date-place {
            margin-top: 0.5in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 1in;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Right to Information (RTI) Application</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <p>To,</p>
            <p>The Public Information Officer (PIO),</p>
            <p><span class="bold underline">{{ public_authority | default("[Name of Public Authority/Department]") }}</span>,</p>
            <p><span class="bold underline">{{ department_address | default("[Address of Public Authority/Department]") }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Subject:</span> Application for information under the Right to Information Act, 2005.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Respected Sir/Madam,</p>
            <p>I, <span class="bold underline">{{ applicant_name | default("[Applicant's Full Name]") }}</span>, son/daughter/wife of <span class="bold underline">{{ applicant_father_name | default("[Applicant's Father/Husband's Name]") }}</span>,
            residing at <span class="bold underline">{{ applicant_address | default("[Applicant's Full Address]") }}</span>, Mobile No. <span class="bold underline">{{ applicant_phone | default("[Applicant's Mobile Number]") }}</span>, Email: <span class="bold underline">{{ applicant_email | default("[Applicant's Email Address]") }}</span>,
            wish to seek the following information under the provisions of the Right to Information Act, 2005:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <ol>
                <li>{{ information_sought_1 | default("[Specific information point 1]") }}</li>
                <li>{{ information_sought_2 | default("[Specific information point 2]") }}</li>
                <li>{{ information_sought_3 | default("[Specific information point 3]") }}</li>
                <!-- Add more points as needed -->
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Period for which information is sought:</span> <span class="underline">{{ period_of_information | default("[e.g., 'From January 1, 2020 to December 31, 2023', 'Last 5 years']") }}</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I am an Indian citizen and I am seeking this information in the public interest for the purpose of <span class="underline">{{ purpose | default("[Purpose of seeking information, e.g., 'understanding government policies', 'ensuring transparency']") }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I have paid the prescribed fee of Rs. <span class="bold underline">{{ payment_amount | default("[Fee Amount]") }}</span> vide <span class="bold underline">{{ payment_details | default("[Payment Method and Details, e.g., 'Indian Postal Order No. XXXXXX', 'Demand Draft No. YYYYYY']") }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I request you to provide the information within the stipulated time frame as per the RTI Act, 2005.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <p class="bold">{{ applicant_name | default("[Applicant's Full Name]") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="date-place">
            <p>Date: {{ date_of_application | default(current_date) }}</p>
            <p>Place: {{ place | default("[Place]") }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
